0.05 (2021-01-28)

    Enhancements:
        - Add a --no-comments option.
        - Various code cleanups and improvements

0.05_1 (2021-01-27)

    API / Behaviour Changes:
        - SQL::Tree function is now just "generate(\%args)" and is not
          exported.
        - sqltree: revamp of all arguments and options

    Enhancements:
        - Modernizing and refactoring. Much better SQLite code.

    Dependencies:
        - Remove a bunch of DBI/DBD::SQLite and Test:: stuff (made
          development requirements)
        - File::ShareDir, OptArgs2, Template::Tiny, Test2::V0, ...

    Packaging:
        - Migrate to ExtUtils::MakeMaker away from Module::Install.

