    API Changes:
        - N/A

    New Features:
        - N/A

    Enhancements:
        - Perltidy and Podtidy all files with new .perltidyrc.

    Bug Fixes:
        - Correctly re-parent path columns on update.
        - Correctly update path columns on 'path_from' update.

0.03 (2010-08-03)

    API Changes:
